#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:1
msgid "Tool 工具系统"
msgstr "Tool Tool system"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:3
msgid "实现功能"
msgstr "Implement functionality"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:5
msgid ""
"SimpleLLMFunc 的工具系统为大语言模型提供了调用外部函数和 API 的能力，让 LLM "
"能够执行计算、查询数据、调用服务等操作。工具系统支持两种创建方式，并能自动将 Python 函数转换为 LLM 可理解的工具描述格式。"
msgstr ""
"The SimpleLLMFunc tool system enables large language models to call external"
" functions and APIs, allowing LLMs to perform operations such as "
"calculations, data queries, and service calls. The tool system supports two "
"creation methods and can automatically convert Python functions into a tool "
"description format understandable by LLMs."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:7
msgid "核心功能特性"
msgstr "Core features"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:8
msgid "**智能类型推断**: 自动从函数签名中提取参数类型和描述信息"
msgstr ""
"**Intelligent Type Inference**: Automatically extract parameter types and "
"descriptions from function signatures"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:9
msgid "**文档字符串解析**: 支持从 docstring 中解析参数描述"
msgstr ""
"**Docstring Parsing**: Supports parsing parameter descriptions from "
"docstrings"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:10
msgid "**JSON Schema 生成**: 自动生成符合 OpenAI Function Calling API 的工具描述"
msgstr ""
"**JSON Schema Generation**: Automatically generate tool descriptions that "
"comply with the OpenAI Function Calling API"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:11
msgid "**类型安全**: 支持基本类型、容器类型、Pydantic 模型等多种类型"
msgstr ""
"**Type safety**: Supports multiple types such as basic types, container "
"types, and Pydantic models."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:12
msgid "**灵活创建**: 支持装饰器和继承两种创建方式"
msgstr ""
"**Flexible Creation**: Supports two creation methods: decorators and "
"inheritance."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:13
msgid "**批量序列化**: 支持将多个工具一次性序列化为 API 格式"
msgstr ""
"**Batch Serialization**: Supports serializing multiple tools into API format"
" at once"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:15
msgid "支持的数据类型（参数类型）"
msgstr "Supported data types (parameter types)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:16
msgid "**基本类型**: `str`, `int`, `float`, `bool`"
msgstr "**Basic Types**: `str`, `int`, `float`, `bool`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:17
msgid "**容器类型**: `List[T]`, `Dict[K, V]`"
msgstr "**Container Type**: `List[T]`, `Dict[K, V]`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:18
msgid "**多模态类型**: `Text`, `ImgPath`, `ImgUrl`"
msgstr "**Multimodal type**: `Text`, `ImgPath`, `ImgUrl`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:19
msgid "**多模态列表**: `List[Text]`, `List[ImgPath]`, `List[ImgUrl]`（由字符串列表自动转换）"
msgstr ""
"**Multimodal List**: `List[Text]`, `List[ImgPath]`, `List[ImgUrl]` "
"(automatically converted from string list)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:20
msgid "**Pydantic 模型**: 自动解析模型字段和验证规则"
msgstr ""
"**Pydantic Models**: Automatically parse model fields and validation rules"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:21
msgid "**可选参数**: 支持带默认值的可选参数"
msgstr ""
"**Optional parameters**: Supports optional parameters with default values"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:22
msgid "**复杂嵌套**: 支持嵌套的容器类型和复杂对象"
msgstr ""
"**Complex nesting**: Supports nested container types and complex objects"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:24
msgid "**⚠️ 注意： 由于LLM提供给工具的参数只能是json支持的类型，所以实际上`Tuple`, `Set`等容器是无法作为工具参数的**"
msgstr ""
"**Warning:** Because parameters passed to the tool by LLM can only be of "
"JSON-supported types, containers such as `Tuple` and `Set` cannot actually "
"be used as tool parameters."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:26
msgid "支持的返回类型"
msgstr "Supported return types"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:27
msgid "工具函数可以返回多种数据格式，系统会自动处理这些返回值并将其传递给 LLM："
msgstr ""
"Tool functions can return multiple data formats, and the system will "
"automatically process these return values and pass them to the LLM:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:29
msgid "基本返回类型"
msgstr "Basic return type"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:30
msgid "**字符串 (`str`)**: 直接作为文本内容返回给 LLM"
msgstr "**String (`str`)**: Directly return as text content to LLM"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:31
msgid "**JSON 可序列化对象**: 包括 `dict`, `list`, `int`, `float`, `bool`, `None`"
msgstr ""
"**JSON serializable object**: including `dict`, `list`, `int`, `float`, "
"`bool`, `None`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:32
msgid "**Pydantic 模型**: 自动序列化为 JSON 格式"
msgstr "**Pydantic Model**: Automatically serialized to JSON format"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:34
msgid "多模态返回类型"
msgstr "Multimodal return type"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:35
msgid "**图片URL (`ImgUrl`)**: 返回网络图片链接，LLM 可以\"看到\"图片内容"
msgstr ""
"**Image URL (`ImgUrl`)**: Returns a network image link, allowing LLMs to "
"\"see\" image content"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:36
msgid "**本地图片 (`ImgPath`)**: 返回本地图片文件路径，自动转换为 base64 格式"
msgstr ""
"**Local image (`ImgPath`)**: Returns the local image file path, "
"automatically converted to base64 format."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:37
msgid ""
"**文本+图片组合 (`Tuple[str, ImgUrl]` 或 `Tuple[str, ImgPath]`)**: 同时返回文本说明和图片"
msgstr ""
"`text` parameter must be a string. You provided `Tuple[str, ImgUrl]` or "
"`Tuple[str, ImgPath]` as the type."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:39
msgid "返回类型示例"
msgstr "Return type example"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:98
msgid "返回类型处理机制"
msgstr "Return type processing mechanism"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:100
msgid "**基本类型**: 直接序列化为 JSON 字符串传递给 LLM"
msgstr ""
"**Basic Type**: Directly serialized into a JSON string and passed to LLM"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:101
msgid "**图片类型**:"
msgstr "Image type:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:102
msgid "`ImgUrl`: 直接使用网络 URL"
msgstr "`ImgUrl`: Use network URL directly"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:103
msgid "`ImgPath`: 自动转换为 base64 编码的 data URL"
msgstr "`ImgPath`: automatically convert to base64 encoded data URL"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:104
msgid "**组合类型**: 将文本和图片组合成多模态消息，LLM 可以同时看到文本说明和图片内容"
msgstr ""
"**Composite type**: Combine text and images into multimodal messages, "
"allowing LLMs to see both text descriptions and image content "
"simultaneously."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:105
msgid "**错误处理**: 不支持的返回类型会自动转换为字符串格式"
msgstr ""
"Error handling: Unsupported return types are automatically converted to "
"string format"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:107
msgid "**多模态返回的特殊处理**："
msgstr "**Special Handling of Multimodal Returns**:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:109
msgid "当工具返回图片或文本+图片组合时，框架会用 **assistant + user** 的多模态消息对替代标准 `tool` 消息"
msgstr ""
"When the tool returns an image or a text+image combination, the framework "
"replaces the standard `tool` message with a **assistant + user** multimodal "
"message pair"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:110
msgid "这是因为 OpenAI tool_call 消息无法直接携带多模态内容"
msgstr ""
"This is because OpenAI tool_call messages cannot directly carry multimodal "
"content"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:111
msgid "因此在事件流与历史中，工具调用会被折叠为一条说明性 assistant 消息与一条包含多模态内容的 user 消息"
msgstr ""
"Therefore, in the event stream and history, tool invocations are collapsed "
"into one explanatory assistant message and one user message containing "
"multimodal content."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:113
msgid "**⚠️ 返回类型注意事项**:"
msgstr "**⚠️ Return Type Notes**:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:114
msgid "确保本地图片文件路径存在且可读"
msgstr "Ensure that the local image file path exists and is readable."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:115
msgid "网络图片 URL 应该是公开可访问的"
msgstr "Network image URLs should be publicly accessible."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:116
msgid ""
"组合类型的元组必须是 `(str, ImgPath)` 或 `(str, ImgUrl)` 格式, "
"不能交换`str`和`ImgPath`/`ImgUrl`的顺序"
msgstr ""
"Tuple types of combinations must be in the format of `(str, ImgPath)` or "
"`(str, ImgUrl)`, the order of `str` and `ImgPath`/`ImgUrl` cannot be "
"swapped."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:117
msgid "避免返回过大的数据结构，以免影响 LLM 处理效率"
msgstr ""
"Avoid returning excessively large data structures to prevent impacting LLM "
"processing efficiency."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:119
msgid "**⚠️ 注意：`@tool` 装饰器要求被装饰的函数本身定义为 `async def`，以便在异步执行链路中无缝协作。**"
msgstr ""
"⚠️ Note: The `@tool` decorator requires the decorated function itself to be "
"defined as `async def` to enable seamless collaboration within asynchronous "
"execution chains."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:121
msgid "内置工具集"
msgstr "Built-in Tools"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:123
msgid "FileToolset（文件工具）"
msgstr "FileToolset (file tools)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:125
msgid "提供安全的文件读取、搜索与编辑能力，带哈希校验以避免陈旧写入。仅允许访问工作区内的非隐藏文件。"
msgstr ""
"Provides secure file reading, searching, and editing capabilities, with hash"
" verification to avoid stale writes. Only allows access to non-hidden files "
"within the workspace."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:127
msgid "**工具列表：**"
msgstr "**Tool List:**"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:129
msgid "`read_file`：读取文件内容，可指定起止行并附带行号"
msgstr ""
"read_file: Read file content, can specify start and end lines with line "
"numbers"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:130
msgid "`grep`：在工作区内进行正则搜索（必须提供 `path_pattern`）"
msgstr ""
"`grep`: performs regex search within the workspace (must provide "
"`path_pattern`)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:131
msgid "`sed`：按行范围进行正则替换（需先 read_file）"
msgstr "`sed`: regex replacement by line range (need to read_file first)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:132
msgid "`echo_into`：覆盖写入整个文件（需先 read_file）"
msgstr "`echo_into`: overwrite the entire file (need to read_file first)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:134
msgid "**使用示例：**"
msgstr "**Usage Example:**"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:147
msgid "**注意事项：**"
msgstr "**Precautions:**"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:149
msgid "修改前务必先 `read_file`，否则会返回 “file has been changed” 提示"
msgstr ""
"Be sure to `read_file` first before modifying, otherwise it will return "
"\"file has been changed\" prompt"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:150
msgid "`grep` 必须提供 `path_pattern` 以限定搜索范围"
msgstr "`grep` must provide `path_pattern` to limit the search scope"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:151
msgid "隐藏文件/目录不可访问"
msgstr "Hidden files/directories are not accessible"

