msgstr "Parameter description"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:197
msgid "@tool 装饰器参数"
msgstr "@tool decorator arguments"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:198
msgid "**name** (必需): 工具名称，应该简洁明了，符合函数命名规范"
msgstr ""
"name (required): Tool name, should be concise and clear, conforming to the "
"function naming convention"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:199
msgid "**description** (必需): 工具的简短描述，说明工具的主要功能"
msgstr ""
"**description** (required): A brief description of the tool, explaining its "
"main functionality"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:200
msgid ""
"**best_practices** (可选): 工具最佳实践提示，`llm_chat` / `llm_function` 会自动注入 system "
"prompt"
msgstr ""
"**best_practices** (optional): Tool best practice tips, `llm_chat` / "
"`llm_function` will automatically inject system prompt"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:201
msgid ""
"**prompt_injection_builder** (可选): 动态注入器，接收上下文并返回一段工具专属的 system prompt 引导"
msgstr ""
"**prompt_injection_builder** (optional): Dynamic injector, receives context "
"and returns a tool-specific system prompt guidance"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:203
