msgstr "Function requirements"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:204
msgid "**类型标注**: 建议为所有参数添加类型标注，以便自动生成准确的 JSON Schema"
msgstr ""
"**Type Annotation**: It is recommended to add type annotations to all "
