msgstr "Tool calling process"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:210
msgid "**工具注册**: 使用 `@tool` 装饰器或继承 `Tool` 类创建工具"
msgstr ""
"Tool Registration: Use the `@tool` decorator or inherit the `Tool` class to "
