msgstr "Tool usage example"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:620
msgid "将 `@llm_function` 暴露为工具（Agent as a Tool）"
msgstr "Expose `@llm_function` as a Tool (Agent as a Tool)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:622
msgid ""
"当你希望一个上层 agent 把下层 specialist 当成工具调用时，可以把 `@tool` 叠加在 `@llm_function` 外层："
msgstr ""
"When you want an upper-level agent to call a lower-level specialist as a "
"tool, you can stack `@tool` on the outer layer of `@llm_function`:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:657
msgid "要点："
msgstr "Key Points:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:659
msgid "推荐顺序写成 `@tool` 外层、`@llm_function` 内层。"
msgstr ""
"Recommend writing the order with `@tool` as the outer layer and "
"`@llm_function` as the inner layer."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:660
msgid ""
"子 agent 推荐使用 `@llm_function(enable_event=False)`，这样它表现为普通 `async` tool。"
msgstr ""
"Sub-agent recommends using `@llm_function(enable_event=False)`, so that it "
"behaves as a regular `async` tool."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:661
msgid "`@llm_chat` 返回的是异步生成器；如果一定要把它当工具复用，通常需要先写一个手动 wrapper。"
msgstr ""
"`@llm_chat` returns an async generator; if you must reuse it as a tool, you "
"usually need to write a manual wrapper first."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:662
msgid "可运行完整示例见 `examples/agent_as_tool_example.py`。"
msgstr ""
"For a runnable complete example, see `examples/agent_as_tool_example.py`."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:664
msgid "高级用法"
msgstr "Advanced usage"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:666
msgid "工具序列化和检查"
msgstr "Tool serialization and inspection"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:683
msgid "动态工具创建"
msgstr "Dynamic tool creation"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:706
msgid "工具链组合"
msgstr "toolchain combination"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:739
msgid "返回类型最佳实践"
msgstr "Best practices for return types"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:741
msgid "选择合适的返回类型"
msgstr "Choose the appropriate return type"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:743
msgid "**文本输出优先**: 如果工具主要产生文本结果，使用 `str` 或结构化的 `Dict`"
msgstr ""
"**Text Output Priority**: If the tool primarily produces text results, use "
"`str` or a structured `Dict`."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:744
msgid "**结构化数据**: 复杂数据使用 `Dict` 或 `List`，便于 LLM 理解和处理"
msgstr ""
"**Structured Data**: Complex data uses `Dict` or `List` for easy "
"understanding and processing by LLM"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:745
msgid "**多模态内容**: 需要展示图片时使用 `ImgPath`、`ImgUrl` 或组合类型"
msgstr ""
"**Multimodal Content**: Use `ImgPath`, `ImgUrl`, or a combination type when "
"displaying images."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/tool.md:746
msgid "**组合输出**: 需要同时提供说明和图片时使用 `Tuple[str, ImgPath/ImgUrl]`"
msgstr ""
"**Combined Output**: Use `Tuple[str, ImgPath/ImgUrl]` when both description "
"and image need to be provided"

